LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       OOH_2.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (14.19 14.19 14.19)
  2 by 2 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  67 atoms
